name: Duane Peabody
text:
Veggie pizza with half anchovies.... 10 minutes for under $12...
. Great pizza... Great service and friendly staff... New clean  store.....extras provided too......would recommend!!! A plus

name: Michelle Luna
text: As i was giving my order, expecting to pay listed price, the gentleman let me know of the deals they had and how upsizing would save me money. I left paying less than what i expected,  and with more food than i had planned on taking home. I was more than pleased with the service, and the pizza was delicious.  Definitely worth the drive.

text: Good pizza, always it's far away from my house, but I stopped to get dinner for my family  ,really good service

name: Linda Lukins
text: Pizza quality varies from order to order, sadly.  It's great most of the time but, occasionally not made well?  Hope they get the consistency down.

text: It's exactly what you would expect from Papa John's Pizza. Sometimes you're craving it and sometimes it's disgusting but it's always exactly the same

text: I went in for a takeout order. The staff were friendly and efficient. Our order was ready in about 10 minutes on a Friday evening. The pizza was good.
